	(63,3,1,209,'<h2>Bristol CT Hotel Reservations - Travel Made Easy</h2>\n\n<p>When you need to make hotel reservations in Bristol, the DoubleTree by Hilton makes business and vacation travel easy and affordable. Our courteous reservations team is always on hand to help you book your stay - weather it&#39;s a family getaway, an essential business meeting or last-minute weekend escape. With our contemporary design, engaging spaces and passionate service, our hotel surrounds you in modern comfort and capability - from the heated atrium pool to the high-tech business center to our trendy dining spots.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Inviting Spaces, Caring People</strong> - Please contact us to make your hotel reservations, plan a special event or take advantage of our unique hotel packages. We look forward to welcoming you to Bristol with our warm smiles and famous freshly-baked cookies.</p>\n','2016-01-07 14:58:20','2016-01-07 14:58:20',1,1,0),
	(53,3,1,219,'<p>Experience the ultimate in dining experience in The Boardroom. Let our Chef create an unparalleled tasting menu for you paired with wines from our boutique list. If you prefer, you may order from The Willows menu, taking advantage of The Boardroom&rsquo;s state of the art technology.</p>\n','2016-01-07 11:42:20','2016-01-07 11:42:20',1,1,0),
