	(44,3,1,222,'<h2>Design Your Meetings &amp; Events to You</h2>\n\n<p>At the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol, planning a meeting or event is all about you. We offers custom meeting and event packages that can designed around your concept, theme and individual style. We understand that life is complex, so have created event packages that make putting together the details seamless and hassle free. Whether you are hosting a corporate conference, business meeting, training session or a fabulous reception, the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol offers all-inclusive meeting and event packages that ensure everything is taken care of - from catering to group activities to special rates on accommodations. When it comes to creating an event in Bristol, Connecticut, we have the resources and tools to make things happen.</p>\n','2016-01-06 16:21:26','2016-01-06 16:21:26',1,1,0),
