	(25,3,1,210,'<h2>Luxury Hotel in Bristol, Connecticut</h2>\n\n<p>Completely renovated in 2013, the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol features a modern urban design, contemporary d&eacute;cor, stylish furnishings and upscale amenities for discriminating travelers. From the moment you arrive at our hotel, you are greeted with New England hospitality, impeccable service and home-like comforts, including a warm chocolate chip cookie to welcome you. Our attentive staff is always there to lend a hand, whether you are relaxing in your room or attending a special event.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Relax, Refresh, Rewind</strong> - Our hotel is the perfect place to relax, rejuvenate, work, dine, meet and celebrate. Take a refreshing dip in our heated indoor swimming pool and bubbling hot tub, and lounge in the relaxing glass-covered atrium. Recharge with an energizing workout in our 24-hour fitness center, or pick up anything you forgot in the Sundries Shop. Whether you are chilling by pool or enjoying a drink at the bar, you are connected with free wireless internet.</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Meeting Place</strong> - Host an important business meeting, seminar, special event or a romantic wedding in Bristol. DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol features over 7,200 sq. ft. of flexible meeting and banquet space, offering advanced AV technology, creative catering, packages and event planning. Catch up on work in our all-hours business center, a high-tech space where you can print a presentation or fax a last-minute project.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Food is Comfort</strong> - Start your day with our Wake Up DoubleTree Breakfast with hot foods and healthy granola, yogurt, and whole-grain cereals and breads. Enjoy a relaxing dinner in The Willows, our inviting restaurant dishing up new American, farm-to-fork cuisine and wines from around the world. Unwind in the warm atmosphere of Time Out, a casual bar where you can meet friends for lunch or evening drinks, and sip craft-brewed beer and flavorful wines. Need a snack on the go? Stop by our Pantry Market.</p>\n\n<h3>Services &amp; Amenities For Every Lifestyle</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>24 Hour Front Desk</li>\n	<li>ATM Audio/Visual Equipment</li>\n	<li>Entirely Non-Smoking Property</li>\n	<li>Bar &ndash; Time Out</li>\n	<li>Hot Breakfast</li>\n	<li>Baggage Storage</li>\n	<li>Business Center &ndash; Fax, Copy, Print</li>\n	<li>Concierge Desk</li>\n	<li>Dry Cleaning Service</li>\n	<li>Express Check-In/Check-Out</li>\n	<li>Free Newspapers (Lobby)</li>\n	<li>Fitness Center</li>\n	<li>Gift Shop &amp; News Stand</li>\n	<li>Hot Tub in Atrium</li>\n	<li>Free Internet &amp; Wireless Access</li>\n	<li>Indoor Atrium Swimming Pool</li>\n	<li>Laundry Facilities</li>\n	<li>Local Area Transportation</li>\n	<li>Meeting &amp; Event Space</li>\n	<li>Pavilion Pantry Market</li>\n	<li>Restaurant &amp; Bar Room Service</li>\n	<li>Safety Deposit Box</li>\n	<li>Television In Lobby</li>\n	<li>Free Parking</li>\n	<li>Handicap Access</li>\n	<li>Video Conferencing</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Check-In Time</strong> - 3:00 pm<br />\n<strong>Check-Out Time</strong> - 12:00 pm</p>\n','2016-01-06 15:28:45','2016-01-06 15:28:45',1,1,0),
