	(51,3,1,221,'<h2>Welcome to The Oaks Ballroom at DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol</h2>\n\n<p>At The Oaks Ballroom at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol, your complete satisfaction is assured&hellip; no detail is overlooked. Our professional event&nbsp;planners have the expertise to create the perfect Wedding, Bar or Bat Mitzvah, Anniversary Party, Retirement Dinner, or any other important&nbsp;gathering.</p>\n\n<p>With nearly 7,500 square feet of event space and state of the art technology,&nbsp;The Oaks Ballroom and our other meeting venues offer our&nbsp;corporate guests nearly unlimited options.</p>\n\n<p>The&nbsp;DoubleTree food and beverage&nbsp;staff excels, creating uncommon menus and libations to complement your event and satisfy even your most discerning guests. Whatever your needs, social or corporate,&nbsp;The Oaks Ballroom at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol is the ideal venue.</p>\n','2016-01-07 11:20:23','2016-01-07 11:20:23',1,1,0),
