	(33,3,1,214,'<h2>Advance Purchase Package</h2>\n\n<p>Planning ahead is the smartest way to save at DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. Make your reservations in advance and save up to 20% off your stay with us. Whether you are planning a family holiday, a business trip or a romantic getaway, we make it easy to escape in style.&nbsp; So book your next getaway and enjoy our outstanding service, beautiful accommodations, complimentary breakfast and a warm chocolate chip cookie when you check in.</p>\n\n<h3>Advance Purchase Package includes</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Complimentary Wake-up&nbsp;DoubleTree Breakfast</li>\n	<li>Warm Chocolate Chip&nbsp;Cookie Welcome</li>\n	<li>20% off Your Stay</li>\n</ul>\n','2016-01-06 15:39:13','2016-01-06 15:39:13',1,1,0),
	(41,3,1,203,'<h2>Meetings &amp; Events in Bristol, CT - Inspired Spaces Where Imagination Lives</h2>\n\n<p>Get connected, stay inspired and celebrate life&#39;s special moments at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol, where events come to life and imagination is infinite. Host an important business meeting, seminar, social event or a romantic wedding at our sophisticated event destination in Bristol - just 20 minutes from Hartford. Our state-of-the-art conference center features over 7,200 square feet of flexible meeting, event and banquet space that can accommodate up to 500 people. Whether you are planning a powerhouse conference, a gala affair or an intimate party of friends, we offer stylish spaces, impeccable service and farm-fresh cuisine that transform your event into a flawless happening!</p>\n\n<p><strong>Corporate Meetings &amp; Conferences</strong> - From board meetings and conferences to trade shows and team building events, DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol delivers a sophisticated and high-tech business experience. Renovated in 2013, our cutting-edge event facility features nine modern meeting rooms, pre-function space and ballrooms with the latest communications and audio/visual technology to enhance your presentations and productions. Our professional meeting planners will work with you to coordinate all the details - from catered breaks to leadership-building activities to group accommodations.&nbsp; We make business work seamlessly.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Exceptional Events Near Hartford</strong> - When it comes to creating a magical special event, our hotel is the place where people come together and celebrations shine.&nbsp; Our inviting, modern spaces are ideal for everything from birthday and anniversary parties to reunions to receptions to company banquets. Whatever you envision, our event planning specialists can select a breathtaking event venue, from our elegant ballrooms to our more intimate banquet salons. With 5,151 sq. ft. of space, The Oaks is a gorgeous backdrop for life&#39;s quintessential festivities.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Romantic Wedding Celebrations </strong>- Celebrate your wedding with friends and family in Bristol. Our hotel offers magnificent spaces and beautiful ballrooms with chic design, style d&eacute;cor, and elegant accents. White linens, glistening candles and colorful flowers create a romantic atmosphere where love and joy blossom. Enjoy a glamorous evening of sumptuous farm-to-table cuisine created by our talented chefs. Our wedding planning team offers personalized service to help you every step of your wedding journey - from catering to decorations to your guest list. We also offer exquisite venues for rehearsal dinners, bridal showers, and bachelor/bachelorette parties.</p>\n','2016-01-06 15:50:04','2016-01-06 15:53:53',1,1,0),
	(29,3,1,212,'<h2>Bed &amp; Breakfast in Bristol</h2>\n\n<p>Enjoy a relaxing bed and breakfast experience at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. You&#39;ll be greeted with a warm chocolate chip cookie welcome and a peaceful night&#39;s sleep in our ultra-comfortable beds. Start your day with our Wake Up DoubleTree Breakfast, with all your morning favorites like hot eggs, sausage, and a variety of healthy foods, including granola, yogurt, and whole grain cereals and breads. Fuel up with a delicious breakfast on the house.</p>\n\n<h3>Bed &amp; Breakfast Package includes</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>DoubleTree Breakfast with Hot Foods</li>\n	<li>Overnight Accommodations</li>\n	<li>Warm Chocolate Chip Cookie Welcome</li>\n</ul>\n','2016-01-06 15:33:39','2016-01-06 15:37:18',1,1,0),
