	(117,3,1,210,'<h2>Luxury Hotel in Bristol, Connecticut with Amenities To Match</h2>\n\n<p>Completely renovated in 2013, the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol features a modern urban design, contemporary d&eacute;cor, stylish furnishings and upscale amenities for modern travelers. From the moment you arrive at our hotel, you are greeted with warm New England hospitality, impeccable service and home-like comforts, including a warm chocolate chip cookie to welcome you. Our attentive staff is always there to lend a hand, whether you are relaxing in your room or attending a special event.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Relax, Refresh, Rewind -&nbsp;</strong>Our hotel is the perfect place to relax, rejuvenate, work, dine, meet and celebrate. Take a dip in our heated indoor salt water swimming pool and bubbling hot tub, then lounge in the relaxing glass-covered atrium. Reinvigorate with an energizing workout in our 24-hour fitness center or pick up anything you forgot in the Sundries Shop. Whether you are chilling by the pool or enjoying a drink at the bar, you can stay connected with free wireless internet.</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Meeting Place -&nbsp;</strong>Host an important business meeting, seminar, special event or a romantic wedding in Bristol. DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol features over 7,200 sq. ft. of flexible meeting and banquet space, offering advanced AV technology, creative catering, packages and event planning. Catch up on work in our all-hours business center, a high-tech space where you can print a presentation or fax a last-minute project.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Food is Comfort -&nbsp;</strong>Start your day with our Wake Up DoubleTree Breakfast that features hot foods and healthy granola, yogurt, whole-grain cereals and breads. Enjoy a relaxing dinner in The Willows, our inviting restaurant dishing up new American, farm-to-fork cuisine and wines from around the world. Unwind in the warm atmosphere of Time Out, a casual bar where you can meet friends for lunch or evening d