	(131,3,1,215,'<h2>AAA Member Discount Package</h2>\n\n<p>Enjoy an unforgettable family road trip and good times in Bristol, Connecticut with your AAA membership. AAA members will enjoy special rates and a warm welcome at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. Enjoy beautiful designer rooms and suites, a hot breakfast every morning and wonderful vacation amenities, including our sparkling atrium pool, fitness center, free WiFi and a warm chocolate chip cookie to greet you when you arrive. So take to the American highways and byways and settle in for some New England hospitality.</p>\n\n<p>When you make your reservations, have your AAA member number ready. Show us your AAA card when you check in and start enjoying the perks of being a AAA member!</p>\n','2016-02-24 12:18:18','2016-02-24 12:18:20',18,18,0),
	(132,3,1,202,'<h2>Dining in Bristol, Connecticut</h2>\n\n<p>Food is comfort. So spoil yourself with a delicious dining experience without leaving our hotel. Indulge in fresh, seasonal cuisine and boutique wines at&nbsp;The Willows, or meet friends at&nbsp;TimeOut&nbsp;for modern gastro-pub fare and craft beer. When the weather is nice, dine al fresco on The Oaks Patio where you can enjoy live entertainment while you sit by the fire pit. Whether you crave farm-to-table cuisine or a juicy burger while you watch the game, the Doubletree by Hilton Bristol features three wonderful restaurants with creative cuisine and distinctive character. Unwind with after-dinner drinks at the bar, or stay in and enjoy in-room dining.</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Willows</strong>&nbsp;- Our farm-to-fork restaurant was carefully created to provide our guests with a unique, locally-sourced experience.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Time Out</strong> - Our casual restaurant and sports bar with classic pub food and an upscale, modern twist.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><strong>The Oaks Patio</strong>&nbsp;- Enjoy our fun, outdoor space with live entertainment, drink specials and comfortable seating.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 22px;\">The Boardroom</strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;- Host your meeting in our elegant boardroom. Dine on our chef&#39;s tasting menu or order from The Willows.</span></p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-24 12:24:53','2016-02-24 12:24:55