	(206,3,1,210,'<h2>Luxury Hotel in Bristol, Connecticut with Amenities To Match</h2>\n\n<p>Completely renovated in 2013, the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol features a modern urban design, contemporary d&eacute;cor, stylish furnishings and upscale amenities for modern travelers. From the moment you arrive at our hotel, you are greeted with warm New England hospitality, impeccable service and home-like comforts, including a warm chocolate chip cookie to welcome you. Our attentive staff is always there to lend a hand, whether you are relaxing in your room or attending a special event.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Relax, Refresh, Rewind -&nbsp;Our hotel is the perfect place to relax, rejuvenate, work, dine, meet and celebrate. Take a dip in our heated indoor salt water swimming pool and bubbling hot tub, then lounge in the relaxing glass-covered atrium. Reinvigorate with an energizing workout in our 24-hour fitness center or pick up anything you forgot in the Sundries Shop. Whether you are chilling by the pool or enjoying a drink at the bar, you can stay connected with free wireless internet.</p>\n\n<p>The Meeting Place -&nbsp;Host an important business meeting, seminar, special event or a romantic wedding in Bristol. DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol features over 7,200 sq. ft. of flexible meeting and banquet space, offering advanced AV technology, creative catering, packages and event planning. Catch up on work in our all-hours business center, a high-tech space where you can print a presentation or fax a last-minute project.</p>\n\n<p>Food Is Comfort -&nbsp;Start your day with our Wake Up DoubleTree Breakfast that features hot foods, as well as healthy granola, yogurt, whole-grain cereals and breads. End your day with a relaxing dinner in The Willows. Our inviting restaurant dishes up new American, farm-to-fork cuisine as well as wines from around the world. You might also choose to unwind in the warm atmosphere of Time Out, a casual bar to meet friends for lunch or evening drinks like craft-brewed beer and flavorful wines. When the weather is warm, enjoy a cocktail and meal out on the Oaks Patio, featuring live entertainment and fire pits. Need a snack on the go? Stop by our Pantry Market.</p>\n\n<h3>Services &amp; Amenities for Every Lifestyle</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>24-Hour Front Desk</li>\n	<li>ATM Audio/Visual Equipment</li>\n	<li>Entirely Non-Smoking Property</li>\n	<li>Bar &ndash; Time Out</li>\n	<li>Hot Breakfast</li>\n	<li>Baggage Storage</li>\n	<li>Business Center &ndash; Fax, Copy, Print</li>\n	<li>Concierge Desk</li>\n	<li>Dry Cleaning Service</li>\n	<li>Express Check-In/Check-Out</li>\n	<li>Free Newspapers (Lobby)</li>\n	<li>Fitness Center</li>\n	<li>Gift Shop &amp; Newsstand</li>\n	<li>Hot Tub in Atrium</li>\n	<li>Free Internet &amp; Wireless Access</li>\n	<li>Indoor Atrium Swimming Pool</li>\n	<li>Laundry Facilities</li>\n	<li>Local Area Transportation</li>\n	<li>Meeting &amp; Event Space</li>\n	<li>Pavilion Pantry Market</li>\n	<li>Restaurant &amp; Bar Room Service</li>\n	<li>Safety Deposit Box</li>\n	<li>Television in Lobby</li>\n	<li>Free Parking</li>\n	<li>Handicap Access</li>\n	<li>Video Conferencing</li>\n	<li>Outdoor Dining</li>\n	<li>Live Music&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-26 10:40:20','2016-02-26 10:40:20',15,15,0),
	(207,3,1,201,'<h2>Great Hotel Deals in Bristol, CT</h2>\n\n<p>Whether you&#39;re looking for a weekend getaway, a family vacation, a romantic weekend or need to travel for business, come take advantage of the exciting hotel specials and travel packages at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. Located just a few minutes from Hartford, our hotel gives you easy access to golf courses, wine trails, museums and family attractions like Lake Compounce - America&#39;s oldest theme park. Enjoy easy escapes to our hotel and experience modern comfort, warm hospitality and great savings with out latest hotel specials. Click on the package for more information.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Bed &amp; Breakfast Package</h3>\n\n<p>Enjoy a relaxing bed and breakfast experience in Bristol. Sleep tight in beautiful rooms and suites with luxury beds and awaken refreshed to a delicious hot breakfast with seasonal foods and fresh artisan coffee.</p>\n\n<h3>Senior Savings Package</h3>\n\n<p>Get your travel adventure off to a wonderful start. Spend the weekend with the grandkids or enjoy a romantic escape that celebrates your golden years. We&#39;ll make sure you create memories of a lifetime.</p>\n\n<h3>Advance Purchase Package</h3>\n\n<p>Make your reservations early and save 20%. Whether you are planning a family vacation or a business trip, escape in style with beautiful accommodations, breakfast and a warm chocolate chip cookie welcome.</p>\n\n<h3>AAA Member Discount Package</h3>\n\n<p>Take to the American roadways for an unforgettable family adventure. AAA members enjoy special rates and warm New England hospitality. Show us your AAA card and discover good times and happy faces.</p>\n','2016-02-26 10:43:05','2016-02-26 10:43:15',15,15,0),
