	(233,3,1,217,'<h2>Farm-to-Fork Cuisine in Bristol, CT</h2>\n\n<p>With its modern design and stylish aesthetic, this is a contemporary restaurant serving creative, new American cuisine, focusing on farm-fresh ingredients. The innovative, seasonal menu features farm-to-fork creations and regional interpretations of steak, seafood and vegetable dishes &ndash; all artfully plated. The menu changes regularly to highlight fresh, local foods of the season. And you can enhance your dining experience with our extensive selection of boutique wines from around the globe.</p>\n\n<p>We have been reviewed by The New York Times, Hartford Magazine and Connecticut Magazine.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The Willows is a proud receipient of the OpenTable Diner&#39;s Choice Award for 2015!&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-29 09:04:45','2016-02-29 09:04:47',1,1,0),
