	(210,3,1,212,'<h2>Enjoy a Romantic Bed &amp; Breakfast in Bristol</h2>\n\n<p>Enjoy a relaxing bed and breakfast experience at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. You&#39;ll be greeted with a warm chocolate chip cookie welcome and a peaceful night&#39;s sleep in our ultra-comfortable beds. Start your day with our Wake Up DoubleTree Breakfast, featuring all of your morning favorites like hot eggs, sausage and a variety of healthy foods including, granola, yogurt, whole grain cereals and breads. Fuel up with a delicious breakfast on the house.</p>\n\n<h3>Bed &amp; Breakfast Package includes:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Complimentary&nbsp;DoubleTree hot breakfast&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Overnight accommodations</li>\n	<li>Warm chocolate chip cookie welcome</li>\n</ul>\n','2016-02-26 10:47:02','2016-02-26 10:47:02',15,15,0),
