	(212,3,1,202,'<h2>Food is Comfort in Bristol, Connecticut</h2>\n\n<p>Spoil yourself with a delicious dining experience without leaving our hotel. Indulge in fresh, seasonal cuisine and boutique wines at&nbsp;The Willows, or meet friends at&nbsp;TimeOut&nbsp;for modern gastro-pub fare and craft beer. When the weather is nice, dine al fresco on the Oaks Patio where you can enjoy live entertainment while you sit by the fire pit. Whether you crave farm-to-fork cuisine or a juicy burger while you watch the game, the Doubletree by Hilton Bristol features three wonderful restaurants with creative cuisine and distinctive character. Unwind with after-dinner drinks at the bar, or stay in and enjoy in-room dining.</p>\n\n<p>The Willows&nbsp;- Our farm-to-fork restaurant was carefully created to provide our guests with a unique, locally-sourced experience.</p>\n\n<p>Time Out - Our casual restaurant and sports bar with classic pub food and an upscale, modern twist.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Oaks Patio&nbsp;- Enjoy our fun, outdoor space with live entertainment, drink specials and comfortable seating.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The Boardroom&nbsp;- Host your meeting in our elegant boardroom. Dine on our chef&#39;s tasting menu or order from The Willows.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-26 10:48:30','2016-02-26 10:48:30',15,15,1),
	(220,3,1,224,'<h2>Exclusive Wedding Menu Packages</h2>\n\n<p>DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol and The Oaks Ballroom has a variety of&nbsp;exquisite venues that will be perfect for your special event. Our wedding planning team offers personalized service to help you every step of your wedding journey &ndash; from catering and decorations to your guest list. We will take care of everything, and you can just enjoy your special day.&nbsp;Our sumptuous farm-to-table cuisine created by our talented chefs can be customized to your personal taste.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Some of our wedding amenities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Chef&#39;s consultation</li>\n	<li>Trusted vendor referrals&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Complimentary menu tasting for two</li>\n	<li>DoubleTree candle centerpieces</li>\n	<li>Private hospitality suite for the bridal party</li>\n	<li>Reception table of regional cheeses, fruits and vegetables&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Butler-passed, deluxe hand-crafted hors d&#39;oeuvres</li>\n	<li>Five-hour hosted bar</li>\n	<li>Champagne toast&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Tableside wine service&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Customized plated or buffet dinner options</li>\n	<li>Cake cutting ceremony&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Wedding night bridal suite and breakfast&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>First-year anniversary suite and celebration dinner</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Click here to view our Wedding Menu Packages.&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-26 11:04:49','2016-02-26 11:04:49',15,15,0),
