	(227,3,1,209,'<h2>Bristol CT Hotel Reservations</h2>\n\n<p>When you need to make hotel reservations in Bristol, the DoubleTree by Hilton makes business and vacation travel easy and affordable. Our courteous reservations team is always on hand to help you book your stay - whether it&#39;s a family getaway, an essential business meeting or last-minute weekend escape. With our contemporary design, engaging spaces and passionate service, our hotel surrounds you in modern comfort and capability - from the heated atrium pool and the high-tech business center to our trendy dining spots.</p>\n\n<p>Inviting Spaces, Caring People - Please contact us to make your hotel reservations, plan a special event or take advantage of our unique hotel packages. We look forward to welcoming you to Bristol with our warm smiles and famous freshly-baked cookies.</p>\n','2016-02-26 11:16:11','2016-02-26 11:16:11',15,15,0),
	(228,3,1,209,'<h2>Bristol CT Hotel Reservations</h2>\n\n<p>When you need to make hotel reservations in Bristol, the DoubleTree by Hilton makes business and vacation travel easy and affordable. Our courteous reservations team is always on hand to help you book your stay - whether it&#39;s a family getaway, an essential business meeting or last-minute weekend escape. With our contemporary design, engaging spaces and passionate service, our hotel surrounds you in modern comfort and capability - from the heated atrium pool and the high-tech business center to our trendy dining spots.</p>\n\n<h3>Inviting Spaces, Caring People</h3>\n\n<p>Please contact us to make your hotel reservations, plan a special event or take advantage of our unique hotel packages. We look forward to welcoming you to Bristol with our warm smiles and famous freshly-baked cookies.</p>\n\n<div class=\"inline_callout left\">42 Century Drive, Bristol, Connecticut 06010</div>\n\n<div class=\"inline_callout left\">860-589-7766</div>\n\n<div class=\"inline_callout left\">FrontDesk.BDLCD@hilton.com</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-26 11:18:18','2016-02-26 11:18:18',15,15,1),
	(225,3,1,208,'<h2>Getting Here Is Easy</h2>\n\n<p>From Hartford&nbsp;-Take I-84 West, take Exit 33 onto Route 72 West toward Bristol. At end of expressway turn left onto Route 229/Middle Street. Go about 1 mile and the hotel is on the right.</p>\n\n<p>From New York City / Danbury&nbsp;- Take I-84 East, take Exit 31, left off ramp onto Route 229/West Street. After about 3 miles, the hotel will be on the left.</p>\n\n<p>From Bradley International Airport&nbsp;- Take I-91 South to I-84 West. Take Exit 33 onto Route 72 West toward Bristol. At end of expressway turn left onto Route 229/Middle Street. Go about 1 mile and the hotel is on the right.</p>\n\n<h3>Hotel in Bristol, Connecticut</h3>\n\n<p>Located in a charming city, midway between New York City and Boston, The DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel Bristol boasts an ideal address for business and leisure travelers. Our convenient hotel is one mile from ESPN Headquarters at the ESPN Plaza and just minutes from trendy shopping, dining and entertainment. Our hotel also offers easy access to local businesses and corporations, downtown Hartford and Bradley International Airport.</p>\n\n<p>Exciting Family Adventures - The DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel Bristol is close to many exciting activities, historic landmarks and attractions. Enjoy a family day trip to Lake Compounce Amusement Park and tour the New England Carousel Museum and Imagine Nation Children&#39;s Museum. Experience the beautiful vineyards and towns along the Connecticut Wine Trail or play on the majestic slopes of the Mt. Southington Ski Area. For outdoor action, explore the Barnes Nature Center and Adventure Balloon Rides.</p>\n\n<h3>Bristol Area Attractions</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Lake Compounce&nbsp;- 1 mile</li>\n	<li>Carousel Museum of New England - 1 mile</li>\n	<li>ESPN Headquarters&nbsp;- 1 mile</li>\n	<li>American Clock and Watch Museum&nbsp;- 1 mile</li>\n	<li>Connecticut Wine Trail&nbsp;- 12.8 miles</li>\n	<li>The Barnes Nature Center&nbsp;- 3 miles</li>\n	<li>Imagine Nation Museum&nbsp;- 3 miles</li>\n	<li>Giamatti Little League Center&nbsp;- 3.5 miles</li>\n	<li>Thomaston Opera House - 7.3 miles</li>\n	<li>Mt. Southington Ski Area&nbsp;- 9.2 miles</li>\n	<li>Repertory Theater of New Britain&nbsp;- 9.3 miles</li>\n	<li>Adventure Balloon Rides&nbsp;- 9.5 miles</li>\n	<li>New Britain Museum of American Art&nbsp;- 10 miles</li>\n	<li>Litchfield Hills&nbsp;- 16.3 miles</li>\n	<li>Warner Theater Torrington&nbsp;- 18 miles</li>\n	<li>CT Science Center&nbsp;- 19 miles</li>\n	<li>Connecticut Convention Center&nbsp;- 20 miles</li>\n	<li>Downtown Hartford&nbsp;- 20 miles</li>\n	<li>Lyman Orchards&nbsp;- 23 miles</li>\n	<li>Lyman Orchards Golf Course&nbsp;- 23 miles</li>\n	<li>Mohegan Sun Casino&nbsp;- 55 miles</li>\n	<li>Foxwoods Casino&nbsp;- 60 miles</li>\n	<li>Bradley International Airport - 35 miles</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n','2016-02-26 11:13:04','2016-02-26 11:13:04',15,15,0),
	(238,3,1,200,'<h2><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Designer Luxury in Bristol for Modern Travelers</span></h2>\n\n<p>All of our rooms and suites feature contemporary design with stylish <span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;\">d&eacute;cor in warm, inviting tones. Located in beautiful Bristol, Connecticut and newly renovated in 2013, our 141 rooms surround you in comfort and convenience.</span>&nbsp;Enjoy a restful sleep in luxurious king or queen beds and wake refreshed for the day ahead. Stay entertained with 42&quot; HDTVs with expanded channels and iHome docking stations. Or catch up with the office with a work desk, wireless internet and two telephones with voicemail. When you need to relax, enjoy CITRON by Crabtree &amp; Evelyn toiletries and a dual-cup Wolfgang Puck coffee maker. Upgrade to a suite and enjoy an added touch of luxury with separate sleeping and living areas for extra space to stretch out.</p>\n\n<p><strong style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Check-In Time</strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;- 3:00 p.m.</span><br />\n<strong style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Check-Out Time</strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;- 12:00 p.m.</span></p>\n\n<p>Learn more about our diverse selection of rooms and suites below:</p>\n\n<h3>King &amp; Queen Standard Room</h3>\n\n<p>The comfort of the Sweet Dreams by DoubleTree plush-top king or 2 queen beds is the centerpiece of this custom-designed room. Lie back on the five jumbo down pillows or relax in the oversized chair with ottoman and flip through more than 60 HD channels on the 42&quot; HDTV. When you need to work, sit at the large desk with an ergonomic executive chair and connect with free high-speed internet. This signature room also features a refrigerator, Keurig coffee maker, iHome docking station and a safe large enough for a laptop. Order up room service and kick back in style.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>1 King Deluxe</h3>\n\n<p>Enjoy a peaceful night&#39;s sleep in Sweet Dreams by DoubleTree plush-top king bed with five jumbo hypo-allergenic down pillows for sublime comfort. This deluxe designer room features all of our standard luxuries, including a Keurig coffee maker, iHome docking station, safe and iron/ironing board. Relax in the comfortable chair with ottoman, flip through 60 channels on the 42&quot; LED TV or tune out with the iHome docking. Stay productive with a large work desk, ergonomic chair and free WiFi. You will feel at home in our deluxe room, which also includes a plush bathrobe, slippers and upgraded bath amenities.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>2 Queen Bed Suite</h3>\n\n<p>This designer two-room suite is an oasis of hospitality where you can work, relax and entertain in modern comfort. Slip into a heavenly sleep in the separate bedroom featuring two plush-top queen beds with five jumbo down pillows, triple sheeted down blanket and cozy coverlet. Sit back and lounge in the chic living room with an overstuffed chair and ottoman, a 42&quot; HDTV with over 60 channels, a wet bar and a plush sofa bed that&#39;s perfect for families with kids. Our spacious suite features a guest bath with a glass enclosed shower. Get down to business at the large desk with an ergonomic chair, telephone with voicemail and complimentary high-speed and wireless internet.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>King Bed Suite</h3>\n\n<p>Located in our Tower, this beautiful one-bedroom suite gives you space and designer luxury you need for work and relaxation on the road. The bedroom features the Sweet Dreams by DoubleTree plush-top king bed with five jumbo down pillows, a triple sheeted down blanket and cozy coverlet so you enjoy home-like comfort. Sit in the stylish living room &ndash; separate from your bedroom &ndash; catch a movie on the 42&quot; HDTV with over 60 channels and prepare a snack or drink at the wet bar. Our luxurious King Suite features a guest bath with a glass enclosed shower. When you need to finish a presentation, there&#39;s a large desk with an ergonomic chair and complimentary high-speed internet access. Relax on the overstuffed chair with an ottoman and take advantage of in-room dining with farm-to-fork cuisine.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>Presidential Suite</h3>\n\n<p>A luxurious sanctuary on the top floor of our Suite Tower, this spectacular 2,000 sq. ft. four-room suite is designed with artful d&eacute;cor and plenty of space to stretch out, relax, work, dine and entertain. The Presidential Suite features a private bedroom with a Sweet Dreams by DoubleTree plush-top king bed with five jumbo hypo-allergenic down pillows. A triple sheeted down blanket and cozy coverlet gives you at-home comfort. Lounge in the spacious living room &ndash; separated from your bedroom by a door &ndash; and enjoy the comfort of your den at home with a 64&quot; HDTV, a dining table for eight, a full kitchen, theatre area and a double sleeper sofa. This luxurious suite features two bathrooms for the guest to enjoy: a half bath, adjacent to the living room, and a full bath, adjacent to the sleeping room, complete with two TVs each housed in its own vanity. When the office calls, stay productive at the functional work space with an ergonomic chair as well as an overstuffed chair with ottoman. Grab a snack from the mini bar or indulge in en-suite dining.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Book Now</a></p>\n','2016-02-29 09:24:11','2016-02-29 09:24:11',1,1,0),
