	(293,3,1,213,'<h2>Discounted Rates for Seniors</h2>\n\n<p>Get your travel adventure off to a great start in Bristol, Connecticut, with our Senior Savings Package. Spend a few days with the grandkids or enjoy a romantic escape that celebrates the passion of your golden years. If you&#39;re 65 years young, we&#39;ll make your welcome even warmer with our Senior Discount Rate. You can even book a second room for the family and make memories that will last a lifetime. Show us your proof of age at check-in and we&#39;ll make your getaway brighter in every way.</p>\n\n<h3>Our Senior Savings Package includes:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Senior discount rate</li>\n	<li>Complimentary DoubleTree hot breakfast&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n','2016-03-01 09:43:07','2016-03-01 09:43:07',15,15,0),
	(219,3,1,204,'<h2>Welcome To the Best Day of Your Life &nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<p>At The Oaks Ballroom, we make dreams become reality. Celebrate this special day in our beautiful and romantic ballroom. Our experienced event planners will make it a day you will never forget. We will customize your reception to match your wildest dreams, whether you want a glamorous evening of white linens, glistening candles and elegant flowers or a rustic DIY event with whimiscal twinkle lights and mason jar centerpieces, the possiblities are endless in The Oaks Ballroom.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>At the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol, brides or grooms get an all-inclusive package deal. Not only will we provide chic design and elegant accents in our beautiful ballroom, but we also offer block room discounts for all your guests as well as exquisite venues for your rehearsal dinner and after-party.&nbsp;Our wedding planning team offers personalized service to help you every step of your wedding journey &ndash; from catering and decorations to your guest list. We will take care of everything, and you can just enjoy your special day.&nbsp;Our sumptuous farm-fresh cuisine created by our talented chefs is anything but typical wedding food, and will have your guests talking about the catering long after your special day.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Trust the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol and The Oaks Ballroom to create an unforgettable event.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','2016-02-26 11:02:52','2016-02-26 11:02:52',15,15,1),
	(224,3,1,207,'<h2>Warm Hospitality with Contemporary Design</h2>\n\n<p>Rated #1 in guest satisfaction among all DoubleTree Hotels in America! With its distinctive style, contemporary design and newly-renovated spaces, The DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel Bristol is a high-end boutique hotel with a unique mix of New England character and high-tech capability. From the moment you walk into our inviting hotel, you are warmly welcomed with a smile and our delicious fresh-baked cookies. Surrounded by the charm of the city, our newly-renovated hotel gives you a sense of home in beautiful Central Connecticut.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n','2016-02-26 11:12:03','2016-02-26 11:12:03',15,15,1),
	(317,3,1,221,'<h2><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/uploads/images/oaksballroom-logo.jpg\" style=\"width: 340px; height: 215px; float: left;\" />Endless Event Possibilities at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol &nbsp;</h2>\n\n<p>At The Oaks Ballroom at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol, your complete satisfaction is assured and no detail is overlooked. Our professional event&nbsp;planners have the expertise to create the perfect wedding, bar or bat mitzvah, wedding or baby shower, retirement dinner or any other important&nbsp;gathering.</p>\n\n<p>With nearly 7,500 square feet of event space and state-of-the-art technology,&nbsp;The Oaks Ballroom and our other meeting venues offer our&nbsp;corporate guests unlimited options.</p>\n\n<p>The&nbsp;DoubleTree food and beverage&nbsp;staff excels, creating uncommon menus and libations to complement your event and satisfy even your most discerning guests. Whatever your needs, social or corporate,&nbsp;The Oaks Ballroom at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol is the ideal venue.</p>\n','2016-03-01 11:19:36','2016-03-01 11:19:36',1,1,0),
