internet access. Relax on the overstuffed chair with an ottoman and take advantage of in-room dining with farm-to-fork cuisine.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>Presidential Suite</h3>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/uploads/images/presidential-suite-doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-th.jpg\" style=\"width: 162px; height: 160px; float: left;\" />A luxurious sanctuary on the top floor of our Suite Tower, this spectacular 2,000 sq. ft. four-room suite is designed with artful d&eacute;cor and plenty of space to stretch out, relax, work, dine and entertain. The Presidential Suite features a private bedroom with a Sweet Dreams by DoubleTree plush-top king bed with five jumbo hypo-allergenic down pillows. A triple sheeted down blanket and cozy coverlet gives you at-home comfort. Lounge in the spacious living room &ndash; separated from your bedroom by a door &ndash; and enjoy the comfort of your den at home with a 64&quot; HDTV, a dining table for eight, a full kitchen, theatre area and a double sleeper sofa. This luxurious suite features two bathrooms for the guest to enjoy: a half bath, adjacent to the living room, and a full bath, adjacent to the sleeping room, complete with two TVs each housed in its own vanity. When the office calls, stay productive at the functional work space with an ergonomic chair as well as an overstuffed chair with ottoman. Grab a snack from the mini bar or indulge in en-suite dining.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px; line-hei