	(354,3,1,201,'<h2>Great Hotel Deals in Bristol, CT</h2>\n\n<p>Whether you&#39;re looking for a weekend getaway, a family vacation, a romantic weekend or need to travel for business, come take advantage of the exciting hotel specials and travel packages at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. Located just a few minutes from Hartford, our hotel gives you easy access to golf courses, wine trails, museums and family attractions like Lake Compounce - America&#39;s oldest theme park. Enjoy easy escapes to our hotel and experience modern comfort, warm hospitality and great savings with out latest hotel specials.</p>\n\n<h3>Bed &amp; Breakfast Package</h3>\n\n<p>Enjoy a relaxing bed and breakfast experience in Bristol. Sleep tight in beautiful rooms and suites with luxury beds and awaken refreshed to a delicious hot breakfast with seasonal foods and fresh artisan coffee.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>Senior Savings Package</h3>\n\n<p>Get your travel adventure off to a wonderful start. Spend the weekend with the grandkids or enjoy a romantic escape that celebrates your golden years. We&#39;ll make sure you create memories of a lifetime.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>Advance Purchase Package</h3>\n\n<p>Make your reservations early and save 20%. Whether you are planning a family vacation or a business trip, escape in style with beautiful accommodations, breakfast and a warm chocolate chip cookie welcome.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>\n\n<h3>AAA Member Discount Package</h3>\n\n<p>Take to the American roadways for an unforgettable family adventure. AAA members enjoy special rates and warm New England hospitality. Show us your AAA card and discover good times and happy faces.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>','2016-05-16 10:43:21','2016-05-16 10:43:21',1,1,1),
	(355,3,1,212,'<h2>Enjoy a Romantic Bed &amp; Breakfast in Bristol</h2>\n\n<p>Enjoy a relaxing bed and breakfast experience at the DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol. You&#39;ll be greeted with a warm chocolate chip cookie welcome and a peaceful night&#39;s sleep in our ultra-comfortable beds. Start your day with our Wake Up DoubleTree Breakfast, featuring all of your morning favorites like hot eggs, sausage and a variety of healthy foods including, granola, yogurt, whole grain cereals and breads. Fuel up with a delicious breakfast on the house.</p>\n\n<h3>Bed &amp; Breakfast Package includes:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Complimentary&nbsp;DoubleTree hot breakfast&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Overnight accommodations</li>\n	<li>Warm chocolate chip cookie welcome</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>','2016-05-16 10:43:30','2016-05-16 10:43:30',1,1,1),
	(356,3,1,213,'<h2>Discounted Rates for Seniors</h2>\n\n<p>Get your travel adventure off to a great start in Bristol, Connecticut, with our Senior Savings Package. Spend a few days with the grandkids or enjoy a romantic escape that celebrates the passion of your golden years. If you&#39;re 65 years young, we&#39;ll make your welcome even warmer with our Senior Discount Rate. You can even book a second room for the family and make memories that will last a lifetime. Show us your proof of age at check-in and we&#39;ll make your getaway brighter in every way.</p>\n\n<h3>Our Senior Savings Package includes:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Senior discount rate</li>\n	<li>Complimentary DoubleTree hot breakfast&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><a class=\"moreBtn\" href=\"http://doubletree3.hilton.com/en/hotels/connecticut/doubletree-by-hilton-hotel-bristol-connecticut-BDLCDDT/index.html\">Book Now</a></p>','2016-05-16 10:43:37','2016-05-16 10:43:37',1,1,1),
