	(3,0,'st-patricks-day-at-timeout','St. Patrick\'s Day at TimeOut','<p>St. Patrick\'s Day at Timeout! Thursday, March 17<sup>th</sup> from 11:00 a.m. until 11:00 p.m. We will have a separate menu available featuring corned beef and cabbage, as well as many other traditional Irish menu items. We will also have beer and drink specials available. </p>\n','Get your green on! Corned beef and cabbage and other traditional Irish items, plus drink specials and more! ','2016-03-17',15,'2016-03-01 09:03:35',1,'2016-04-04 13:55:22'),
	(4,0,'easter-brunch-at-willows','Easter Brunch at The Willows ','<p>Enjoy a traditional Easter Brunch in The Willows on Sunday March 27<sup>th</sup> from 11:00 a.m. - 3:00 p.m. We will be serving a traditional Easter menu. Reservations can be made by calling 860-584-7673. The prices are as follows; they do not include tax or 20% gratuity.</p>\n\n<p>Children = 0-4 years (free)</p>\n\n<p>Kid = 5-12 years ($18.00)</p>\n\n<p>Adults = 13 + years ($39.95)</p>\n','Happy Easter! Join us for a traditional Easter brunch from 11:00 am - 3:00 pm. Reservations are required. ','2016-03-27',15,'2016-03-01 09:03:21',NULL,'2016-04-04 13:55:19'),
	(5,2,'voted-best-hotel-dining','Voted Best Hotel Dining','<p class=\"p1\"><b>Get ready to bite into the restaurants judged the best of the best in Connecticut by our “experts,” who range from veteran restaurant critics and food writers to contemporary bloggers who track the trends as well as the hottest, newest places. Joined by some food-savvy Connecticut Magazine editors, it’s a group for which dining is a passion—and dining at the best places is an art that takes constantly having a collective finger on the pulse of the Connecticut dining scene. Together, our Readers’ Choice and Experts’ Picks provide a comprehensive view of the state’s tastiest places to eat well.</b> <a href=\"http://www.connecticutmag.com/Blog/The-Connecticut-Table/January-2016/Best-Restaurants-in-Connecticut-2016-Experts-Picks/\">Click here to see The Willows on the list. </a></p>\n','Connecticut Magazine voted The Willows, \"Best Hotel Dining\" on their 2016 list of Best Restaurants in Connecticut. ','2016-01-16',15,'2016-03-01 09:03:11',NULL,'2017-06-02 09:53:52'),
	(6,1,'willows-restaurant-featured-on-wfsb-better-ct','The Willows Restaurant Featured on WFSB Better CT','<p>Located in Bristol, The Willows Restaurant is an award winning restaurant that’s getting rave reviews from the New York Times.</p>\n\n<p>View the video on <a href=\"http://www.wfsb.com/story/31165262/fine-dining-at-the-willows-in-bristol\" title=\"WFSB 3 Connecticut\">WFSB 3 Connecticut</a></p>\n','Located in Bristol, The Willows Restaurant is an award winning restaurant that’s getting rave reviews.','2016-02-08',1,'2016-03-21 11:03:50',20,'2017-04-10 13:56:29'),
	(7,1,'ncaa-tournament-championship-game','NCAA Tournament Championship Game','<p>Even if your bracket is busted, come find out who will take home the NCAA Tournament title! TimeOut will be showing Villanova take on North Carolina with food and drink specials throughout the night. TimeOut has multiple large screen televisions for every fan. Come by and root for the underdog Villanova or the top seed Tar Heels! </p>\n','Even if your bracket is busted, come find out who will take home the NCAA Tournament title! Monday April, 4th, TimeOut will be showing Villanova take on North Carolina with food and drink specials throughout the night. ','2016-04-04',15,'2016-04-04 13:04:25',15,'2016-05-09 14:07:14'),
	(8,2,'sommelier-series-class-wine-tasting-2-in-depth-tasting-and-blind-taste-test','Sommelier Series Class: Wine Tasting 2: In Depth Tasting and Blind Taste Test','<p>Join us for the last of four series of sommelier classes that will teach you more about wine! The fourth class is an in-depth tasting and blind taste test. Reservations can be made by calling Aaron at 860.584.7680. </p>\n\n<p>Each class is $40 or $120 for all four classes.</p>\n\n<p>Here is the schedule for the series:</p>\n\n<p>5/26 - Food and Wine Pairing</p>\n\n<p>6/23 - Old World Wines vs. New World Wines: A Compare And Contrast</p>\n\n<p>7/21 - Wine Tasting 2: In-Depth Tasting and Blind Taste Test </p>\n','Join us for our last sommelier series class on July 21, where we\'ll teach you everything you need to know about wine! ','2016-07-21',15,'2016-04-04 13:04:52',21,'2016-07-22 09:25:59'),
	(9,1,'flavors-ct','Flavors of CT','<p>Flavors of Connecticut is an annual signature fundraising event of the American Liver Foundation that stars the best chefs in Connecticut who prepare a five-course meal table-side for 12 guests, complete with wine pairings and service. The chefs have an opportunity to showcase their finest, most creative cuisine to guests who are eager to experience a evening of culinary bliss. Proceeds go to the American Liver Foundation. </p>\n\n<p>Join us for a night that you won\'t soon forget all while helping to improve the lives of the 30 million people in the United States living with liver disease. Go to http://go.liverfoundation.org/site/TR?fr_id=5374&amp;amp;pg=entry to learn more. </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Join us for the annual Flavors of CT with our very own chef Alexia Fliss on Tuesday April 12th! Indulge in a five-course meal complete with wine pairings and service. Proceeds to go to the American Liver Foundation. ','2016-04-12',15,'2016-04-04 15:04:13',NULL,'2016-04-25 16:17:48'),
	(10,1,'mors-day-brunch','Mother\'s Day Brunch','<p><span style=\"color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Georgia, \'Droid Serif\', serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:27px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Join us from 11 a.m. to 3 p.m. for Mother\'s Day Brunch at DoubleTree Bristol. The menu includes pastries, breakfast items, a Belgian buttermilk waffle station, carving station with maple-glazed ham and herb-roasted top sirloin; main courses of fillet of lemon sole, roasted turkey breast and marinated grilled chicken; salads, vegetable sides and a dessert display. Cost is $39.95 for adults, $18 for children ages 5 to 12. Children 4 and under are free. Reservations suggested. 860-584-7673</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Georgia, \'Droid Serif\', serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:27px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">View our Mother\'s Day Brunch menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/Mother\'s_Day-2016.pdf\">here</a></span></p>\n','Make lasting memories with mom at DoubleTree’s Mother’s Day Brunch','2016-05-08',20,'2016-04-25 16:04:17',19,'2016-05-09 14:13:40'),
	(11,2,'beer-dinner-with-long-trail-brewery','Beer Dinner with Long Trail Brewery ','<p>Enjoy a 5-Course Beer Dinner with pairings from Long Trail Brewing Co. This dinner will take place on May 19 on our patio during “National Craft Brew Week”.</p>\n','Enjoy a 5-Course Beer Dinner with pairings from Long Trail Brewing Co. ','2016-05-19',20,'2016-05-09 14:05:14',NULL,'2016-05-20 08:52:37'),
	(12,2,'friday-night-acoustic-summer-series','Friday Night Acoustic Summer Series','<p>Join us on the Oaks Patio starting on Friday, May 27! Every Friday night until September 29, we will be serving drink specials, food specials and have live performances. </p>\n\n<p>Click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/The_Patio_2016_band_scheduleV2.pdf\">here</a> to view the band schedule.</p>\n','Join us on the Oaks Patio starting on Friday, May 27! Every Friday night until September 29, we will be serving drink specials, food specials and have live performances. ','2016-05-18',20,'2016-05-18 10:05:15',NULL,'2016-06-22 11:12:57'),
	(13,2,'roses-on-patio','Roses on the Patio','<p>$55 per person includes 5 different Rose wines, passed appetizers and light food. Music to set the mood, shaded and sunny areas available.</p>\n\n<p>Make sure to RSVP at 860-584-7680</p>\n\n<p>Click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/RoseDinner_4x6%5B1%5D.pdf\">here</a> to view the menu!</p>\n','Join us on Thursday, June 16th at 6pm for Rose Wines on the Patio!','2016-06-16',19,'2016-06-13 16:06:05',19,'2016-06-20 14:58:26'),
	(14,2,'fars-day-dinner-specials-at-willows-restaurant','Father\'s Day Dinner Specials at The Willows Restaurant','<p>Join us on Friday, June 17th and Saturday, June 18th from 6pm - 10pm in The Willows Restaurant. You can find us on Open Table to score points or simply call 860-584-7680 to make a reservation.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Menu specials include:</p>\n\n<p><strong>Surf &amp; Turf</strong></p>\n\n<p><em>14oz Prime Rib, Crabmeat Stuffed Shrimp, Roasted Garlic Mashed Potatoes, Summer Vegetable Medley $42</em></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>House Made Tagliatelle Pasta</strong></p>\n\n<p><em>Braised Short Ribs, Vegetable Medley $27</em></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Grilled Mahi Mahi</strong></p>\n\n<p><em>Tropical Salsa, Jaded Jasmine Rice, Summer Vegetable Medley $29</em></p>\n','Join us on Friday, June 17th and Saturday, June 18th in The Willows Restaurant and enjoy menu specials for Father\'s Day!','2016-06-17',19,'2016-06-16 12:06:30',19,'2016-06-20 14:51:45'),
	(15,2,'sam-adams-tap-takeover','Sam Adams Tap Takeover','<p>We\'re gearing up for a tap takeover with Sam Adams on June 30! Get free t-shirts, glasses and swag and enjoy 3 different tap lines of seasonal beer.</p>\n','Sam Adams Tap Takeover, June 30 at 6pm in Time Out Sports Bar','2016-06-30',19,'2016-06-21 15:06:07',NULL,'2016-07-01 11:43:29'),
	(16,2,'3rd-annual-car-show','3rd Annual Car Show','<p>On Sunday, July 3 from 11am - 4pm, enjoy BBQ and beverages while you check out amazing cars from around the state. Admission is FREE, while a portion of food and beverage proceeds goes towards the Special Olympics of CT.</p>\n','Join us for the 3rd Annual Car Show on Sunday July 3 hosted by the Bristol Police Department and DoubleTree Hotel!','2016-07-03',19,'2016-06-29 15:06:31',19,'2016-07-05 14:06:48'),
	(17,2,'luau-on-patio','Luau on the Patio','<p>Please join us on Friday, July 29 from 6pm - 9pm for a special Hawaiian themed Luau on the Patio. There will be a live performance by Acoustic Marship and a special à la carte food and drink menu. Come with your luau attire!</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/LUAU_MENU_2016.pdf\">here</a> for the Luau menu</p>\n','Friday, July 29 6pm - 9pm Hawaiian themed Luau on the Patio!','2016-07-29',19,'2016-07-12 14:07:51',19,'2016-08-01 09:03:25'),
	(18,2,'goose-island-tap-takeover','Goose Island Tap Takeover','<p>Please join us on Thursday, July 28 from 6pm - 9pm in the TimeOut Sports Bar for a tap takeover by Goose Island. 3 tap lines, featured a special Cask aged beer. Live music by Tom Scarola and giveaways such as glasses, tshirts and stickers.</p>\n','Thursday, July 28 6pm - 9pm in the TimeOut Sports Bar','2016-07-28',19,'2016-07-12 14:07:56',NULL,'2016-07-27 20:08:54'),
	(19,2,'long-trail-tap-takeover','Long Trail Tap Takeover','<p>5 great tap lines from Long Trail Brewing Company (Green Blaze IPA, Limbo IPA, Cranberry Gose, Unearthed Stout, Double Bag). A representative from the brewery will be handing out swag including glasses, t-shirts and hats and talking about the different styles of beer. This event will be held in Time Out Sports Bar.</p>\n','Join us for the Long Trail tap takeover on Thursday, August 25 from 6pm - 9pm!','2016-08-25',19,'2016-08-05 09:08:09',19,'2016-08-26 10:08:17'),
	(20,2,'new-england-clam-bake','New England Clam Bake','<p class=\"p1\">Don\'t miss your chance for one last New England clam bake this summer! We\'ll be featuring an á la carte food menu featuring traditional New England far such as clams, mussels, potatoes and corn on the cob, as well as live acoustic music by Acoustic Marsh Pit.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p1\">Menu:</p>\n\n<p class=\"p1\">Full clam bake - Littlenecks, Steamers, Shrimp, Mussels, Kielbasa, Corn on the Cob, Potatoes...$26 </p>\n\n<p class=\"p1\">Cheeseburger...$6</p>\n\n<p class=\"p1\">Hot Dog...$5</p>\n\n<p class=\"p2\">Bratwurst...$5</p>\n\n<p class=\"p2\">Chicken Sandwich...$6</p>\n','Join us for a New England style Clam Bake on The Patio Friday, August 26 from 6:30pm - 10pm!','2016-08-26',19,'2016-08-05 09:08:06',21,'2016-08-29 12:55:12'),
	(21,2,'augustseptember-2016-pre-fixe-menu','August/September 2016 Pre-Fixe Menu','<p>Join us for dinner at The Willows Restaurant, 8/19 - 9/14 for a special pre-fixe menu. Price is $30/person and wine pairings are available for an additional charge.</p>\n\n<p>Click <a href=\"http://doubletreebristol.com/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_08_2016_PreFixeMenu.pdf\">here</a> to view our menu!</p>\n','The Willows Restaurant pre-fixe menu available 8/19 - 9/14','2016-08-19',19,'2016-08-16 14:08:43',NULL,'2016-09-15 10:34:21'),
	(22,2,'jlohr-wine-dinner','J.Lohr Wine Dinner','<p>You’re invited to our J. Lohr Wine Dinner!</p>\n\n<p>Friday, October 28 at 6 p.m.</p>\n\n<p>$75 per person + gratuity</p>\n\n<p>Enjoy a variety of wine tastings paired with light appetizers.</p>\n\n<p>Reservations with a 50% credit card deposit required. Call 860.584.7663.</p>\n\n<p>Click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/JLohrWineDinner.pdf\">here</a> for the menu</p>\n','Join us for a J.Lohr Wine Dinner on Friday, October 28 at 6pm in The Willows!','2016-10-28',19,'2016-09-01 13:09:26',19,'2016-10-31 12:11:35'),
	(23,2,'holiday-party-savings','Holiday Party Savings','<p>Book your holiday party in one of our beautiful banquet rooms before 9/15 and we\'ll waive the room rental fee, provide a free crudités for the event and offer 10% off your overnight stay!</p>\n\n<p>Call 860.584.7673 for more details.</p>\n','Book your holiday party before 9/15 and save!','2016-09-06',19,'2016-09-06 14:09:44',NULL,'2016-09-19 14:26:16'),
	(24,2,'oktoberfest-tap-takeover','Oktoberfest Tap Takeover','<p>We\'ll be hosting a Tap Takeover in our TimeOut Sports Bar pitting American Oktoberfest beers against the mightly German Oktoberfests.</p>\n\n<p>In the American corner, we\'re tapping Sam Adams and Goose Island, and in the German corner it\'s Oktoberfest classics from Spaten and Hofbrau. </p>\n','Join us on Thursday, September 29 from 6pm - 9pm and celebrate the fall season with our favorite tradition - Oktoberfest!','2016-09-29',19,'2016-09-15 10:09:57',NULL,'2016-09-30 10:17:20'),
	(25,2,'thanksgiving-day-dinner','Thanksgiving Day Dinner','<p>11:30am - 4:30pm</p>\n\n<p>For reservations, call 860-584-7673</p>\n\n<p>Adults: $39.95<br />\nChildren under 12: $18<br />\nChildren under 5: FREE</p>\n\n<p>For our menu, click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/BDT_11_2016_Thanksgiving-Menu.pdf\">here</a></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Join us on Thursday, November 24 for a special Thanksgiving Day dinner!','2016-11-24',19,'2016-09-21 15:09:30',19,'2016-11-28 14:23:36'),
	(26,2,'holiday-parties-at-doubletree-bristol','Holiday Parties at DoubleTree Bristol','<p>The most wonderful time of the year starts here!</p>\n\n<p>Our expert event planners are ready to help you plan your holiday party. For more information please call 860.584.7673 to speak with one of our event planners. Click <a href=\"/meetings-events/oaks-ballroom\">here</a> to view details of our ballroom and 2016 Dinner Menu.<br />\n- Farm-to-table cuisine<br />\n- Ballrooms and banquet facilities<br />\n- Professional event planners</p>\n\n<p>We are also hosting our annual Small Business Holiday Party on Friday, December 9, 2016. Click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/small_business_holiday_flyer_2016.pdf\">here</a> for more details!</p>\n','Let us host your personal or corporate holiday party!','2016-12-09',19,'2016-09-30 12:09:59',NULL,'2017-02-09 12:01:07'),
	(27,2,'homecoming-hopfest','Homecoming HopFest','<p>Enjoy brewers from the Northeast and the sounds of Bristol\'s favorite band, Acoustic Marshpit.<br />\nPartial proceeds from ticket sales will benefit the United Way Chapter of West Central Connecticut taskforce for ending homelessness in CT.</p>\n\n<p>Tickets are available in advance at a discount.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.brownpapertickets.com/event/2699174\">Purchase tickets today!</a></p>\n','Join us for our Homecoming HopFest on Saturday, November 26 from 12pm - 4pm. You can enjoy tastings from over 20 breweries around the Northeast. ','2016-11-26',19,'2016-10-19 11:10:13',NULL,'2016-10-19 11:17:13'),
	(28,2,'new-years-eve-dinner-and-dancing','New Years Eve Dinner and Dancing','<p><img alt=\"DoubleTree Bristol CT New Years Eve\" src=\"http://www.doubletreebristol.com/assets/uploads/images/homepage/specials/home-newyears-champaign.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><u><strong>Join us for the biggest and best New Year’s Eve party in Connecticut!</strong> </u><br /><br />\nOur New Year’s Eve Dinner and Dancing celebration has everything you need to enter 2017 in style: a four course Chef’s Dinner, open bar, hors d’oeuvres, raw bar, live music and, of course, a Champagne toast when the ball drops. Make your New Year’s Eve one to remember at DoubleTree Bristol!</p>\n\n<p><strong>New Year’s Eve Dinner and Dancing</strong><br />\nSaturday, December 31, 2016<br />\n7pm - 12:30am<br />\n$300/couple, $150/individual</p>\n\n<p><strong>Featuring:</strong><br />\n- Champagne<br />\n- Raw Bar and Hors d\'Oeuvres Reception<br />\n- Four course Chef\'s Dinner (menu link below)<br />\n- Open Bar<br />\n- Live music by Shaded Soul (Hartford Magazine’s 2016 Reader’s Choice for Best Band)</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.doubletreebristol.com/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/BDT_2017_01_NYE-Menu.pdf\">View our Four course Chef\'s Dinner menu</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>For reservations call 860-584-7673</strong>. Overnight accommodations are available upon request for an additional charge - this charge includes the New Year\'s Day breakfast buffet.</p>\n\n<p>DoubleTree by Hilton Bristol<br />\n42 Century Drive<br />\nBristol, CT 06010</p>\n','Join us for an evening of fine dining and cocktails!','2016-12-31',19,'2016-10-31 13:10:17',21,'2016-12-06 16:47:26'),
	(29,2,'3-course-prix-fixe-dinner','3-Course Prix-Fixe Dinner','<p>Please join us starting Thursday, December 1 thru Friday, December 30 for a special 3-course prix-fixe dinner. Price is $40/person. To view our menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_12_2016_prix-fixeMenu.pdf\">click here</a>.</p>\n','3-course prix-fixe dinner going on now at The Willows Restaurant!','2016-12-01',19,'2016-12-01 16:12:47',19,'2017-01-04 10:52:22'),
	(30,2,'music-martinis','Music &amp; Martinis','<p>Join us on Thursday, December 22 for a special event sponsored by Belvedere Vodka. We\'re serving up $5 martinis, along with free samples, food specials and live music by the Mass-Conn-Fusion Duo from 5-9pm.</p>\n','$5 Martinis sponsored by Belvedere Vodka','2016-12-22',19,'2016-12-19 10:12:13',NULL,'2016-12-27 14:07:51'),
	(31,2,'bristol-beat-article','Bristol Beat Article','<p>DoubleTree Bristol was featured in a recent edition of The Bristol Beat! Check out the full article as well as the compliation video <a href=\"http://www.centralctchambers.org/news/newsarticledisplay.aspx?ArticleID=212\">here!</a></p>\n','Check out our featured article in the Bristol Beat!','2016-12-27',19,'2016-12-27 14:12:22',NULL,'2017-01-06 09:25:30'),
	(32,2,'nfl-tailgate-party','NFL Tailgate Party','<p>This tailgate kicks off with our Football Sunday All-Day Happy Hour menu available all weekend long – only it’s bigger and better for the playoffs – with double the food for the same low price! And no matter what team you’re cheering for, everyone wins with half price house wines, draft beers and well drinks!</p>\n\n<p>View our menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/BDT_09_2016_Football-Sunday.pdf\">here!</a></p>\n','Let\'s tailgate! Every Saturday and Sunday during the playoffs enjoy double the drinks, double the food and double the fun!','2017-01-07',19,'2017-01-04 10:01:55',NULL,'2017-02-09 11:59:30'),
	(33,2,'valentines-day-special-prix-fixe-menu','Valentine\'s Day Special Prix Fixe Menu','<p>Celebrate your Valentine\'s Day in style at the best restaurant in Bristol, CT!<br />\nJoin us in The Willows Restaurant for a special prix-fixe Valentine\'s Day menu. $65/person for 3 courses plus an additional $35/person for wine pairings. Available 2/10 - 2/14.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_01_2017_ValentineMenu_(1).pdf\">View our menu!</a></p>\n','Join us for a special Valentine\'s Day prix fixe menu available Friday, February 10 - Tuesday, February 14.','2017-02-11',19,'2017-01-04 15:01:23',19,'2017-01-04 15:51:02'),
	(34,2,'tuesday-nights-are-ladies-nights','Tuesday Nights Are Girls\' Night Out!','<p><img alt=\"o-GIRLS-NIGHT-OUT-facebook.jpg\" src=\"http://i.huffpost.com/gen/1955855/images/o-GIRLS-NIGHT-OUT-facebook.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n\n<p>It\'s official - Tuesday night is Girls\' Night Out!</p>\n\n<p>Every Tuesday night through March, we\'re offering a $25 prix-fixe menu for three gourmet courses at The Willows Restaurant. It\'s the best deal in Connecticut! To make your reservation, call 860.584.7663. </p>\n\n<p>View the full special menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_01_2017_GirlsNightOutMenu.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n','Every Tuesday evening from January 10 - March 28, DoubleTree Bristol\'s chef has a special Prix Fixe menu that makes for an extra-special Girls\' Night Out!','2017-03-07',19,'2017-01-06 09:01:18',21,'2017-03-30 14:56:19'),
	(35,2,'st-patricks-day-specials','St. Patrick\'s Day Special Menu','<p>You must have the luck of the Irish - you\'re invited to enjoy an unbeatable St. Patrick\'s Day menu at The Willows and TimeOut Sports Bar! Join us on Friday, March 17 - Sunday, March 19 for a traditional but upscale Irish menu. Call 860.584.7663 to make reservations!</p>\n\n<p>View the full Irish menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_01_2017_StPatricksDayMenu.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n','Celebrate St. Patrick\'s Day at DoubleTree Bristol!','2017-03-17',19,'2017-01-11 12:01:34',21,'2017-03-22 10:37:32'),
	(36,2,'martinis-and-music-series','Martinis and Music Series','<p>Make the most of your Thirsty Thursdays with our Martinis &amp; Music series! We\'re featuring drink specials, food specials and live music  every Thursday night through April, right here at TimeOut Sports Bar! <br /><br />\nApril 6 - Tom Scarola<br />\nApril 20 - Mass-Conn-Fusion<br />\nApril 27 - Marty Q<br />\nMay 4 - GDSaxPlayer<br />\nMay 11 - Bryan MacDonald<br />\nMay 18 - Tom Scarola</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.doubletreebristol.com/dining-drinks/timeout-sports-bar\">Click here to see our TimeOut food and drink menu</a> (specials not included).</p>\n','Every Thursday night stop by for drink specials, food specials and live music!','2017-03-09',19,'2017-02-09 12:02:57',19,'2017-05-26 09:22:50'),
	(37,2,'march-madness','March Madness','<p><img alt=\"Bracket.jpg\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.thefeministwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Bracket.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n\n<p>Are you mad for March Madness? We\'re offering half price house wine and draft beer with food specials at TimeOut Sports Bar during all of the games, along with our big screen HD TVs. Don\'t miss a single buzzer beater! Available during the entire NCAA Tournament, March 14 - April 3.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.doubletreebristol.com/dining-drinks/timeout-sports-bar\">Click here to see our TimeOut Sports bar food and drink menus </a>(specials not included).</p>\n','Come watch the NCAA Tournament at DoubleTree Bristol!','2017-03-14',19,'2017-02-16 14:02:12',21,'2017-02-23 16:59:26'),
	(38,2,'easter-brunch','Easter Brunch','<p>DoubleTree Bristol will be hosting a special Easter Brunch on Sunday, April 16 from 11am - 3pm. Price is $39 for adults and $14 for children under 12. <strong>Reservations are required - 860.584.7673.</strong><br /><br />\nWe will be serving a wide variety of delicious foods including a house-made pastry and bakery selection, omlet station, waffle station and carving station. <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_02_2017_EasterMenu.pdf\">Click here to view our full menu.</a></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Join us for a special Easter Brunch on Sunday, April 16 in The Oaks Ballroom','2017-04-16',19,'2017-03-22 10:03:15',19,'2017-04-04 15:06:27'),
	(39,2,'new-spring-drink-menu','New Spring Drink Menu','<p>Take a look at our new offerings <a href=\"/dining-drinks/timeout-sports-bar\">here</a> and stop into our TimeOut Sports Bar and The Willows Restaurant to give them a try!</p>\n','It\'s finally spring and we\'re celebrating with some new, delicious cocktails!','2017-03-30',19,'2017-03-30 14:03:23',NULL,'2017-06-06 09:27:07'),
	(40,2,'thimble-island-tap-takeover','Thimble Island Tap Takeover','<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">We\'re gearing up for a tap takeover with Thimble Island Brewing Company on April 13! Get free t-shirts, glasses and swag and enjoy a variety of different tap lines of special locally brewed beer.</span></p>\n','Thursday, April 13 6pm - 9pm in TimeOut Sports Bar','2017-04-13',19,'2017-04-10 13:04:10',NULL,'2017-04-14 13:56:33'),
	(41,2,'mors-day-brunch-2017','Mother\'s Day Brunch 2017','<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia, \'Droid Serif\', serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;line-height:27px;color:rgb(51,51,51);background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Join us from 11am to 3pm on Sunday, May 14 for Mother\'s Day Brunch at DoubleTree Bristol. The menu includes pastries, breakfast items, a Belgian buttermilk waffle station, carving station with oven roasted turkey breast and char grilled flat iron steak; main courses of chicken saltimbocca prosciutto and cod provencal; salads, vegetable sides and a dessert display. Cost is $39 for adults and $14 for children under 12. Reservations are required. 860-584-7673</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia, \'Droid Serif\', serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;line-height:27px;color:rgb(51,51,51);background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">View our Mother\'s Day Brunch menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/BDT_04_2017_MothersDayMenu.pdf\">here.</a></span></p>\n','Make lasting memories with mom at DoubleTree\'s Mother\'s Day Brunch!','2017-05-14',19,'2017-04-14 14:04:04',19,'2017-04-17 10:46:41'),
	(42,2,'dine-charity-table','Dine for Charity Table','<p>Help us #MakeJunePurple by reserving our Dine for Charity table at The Willows Restaurant. When you do, for the entire month of June, 10% of your total bill will go to our Alzheimer\'s Association Connecticut Chapter. Make your reservation today, 860-584-7663.</p>\n','June is Alzheimer\'s &amp; Brain Awareness Month. Reserve our Dining for Charity table all month and 10% goes to the Alzheimer\'s Association Connecticut Chapter.','2017-06-01',19,'2017-05-01 16:05:03',19,'2017-06-06 09:34:26'),
	(43,2,'cinco-de-mayo','Cinco de Mayo ','<p>Get ready to shake your maracas at TimeOut Sports Bar and The Willows Restaurant Friday, May 5 - all day and night!</p>\n\n<p>We have two special drinks ready just for you! Our classic margarita made with Espolon Silver tequila, cointreau, lime/lemon juice and simple syrup as well as Dani\'s Day Off made with Espolon Reposado tequila, mango puree, lime/lemon juice and jalapeno syrup. <br /><br />\nIn addition to our regular menu, a special Cinco de Mayo menu will also be available. To view our specials, <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/BDT_05_2017_CincoDeMayoMenu-2.pdf\">click here.</a><br />\n </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Come celebrate Cinco de Mayo DoubleTree Bristol style!','2017-05-05',19,'2017-05-02 13:05:01',NULL,'2017-05-09 09:26:45'),
	(44,2,'wehavecookies','#wehavecookies','<p>On Monday, May 15 stop in to our hotel for a free chocolate chip cookie along with other special cookie-themed drinks and desserts. Upon check-in, use #wehavecookies to join in on the conversation. This is a day that is being celebrated by DoubleTree hotels around the world! Want to enjoy our signature cookie all year round? Visit doubletreecokies.com for featured recipes. Hope to see you there!</p>\n','May 15 is National Chocolate Chip Day. Join in on the fun with DoubleTree Bristol! #wehavecookies','2017-05-15',19,'2017-05-09 10:05:04',NULL,'2017-05-16 09:32:59'),
	(45,2,'2017-friday-night-acoustic-summer-series','2017 Friday Night Acoustic Summer Series','<p>Outdoor patio season has officially started in CT! Join us on the Oaks Patio starting Friday, May 26! Every Friday night through September from 6:30pm - 10pm, we will be serving drink and food specials along with live acoustic music performances. View our complete schedule <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/2017_-_Band_Music_schedule.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n','Join us on the Oaks Patio starting Friday, May 26! ','2017-05-26',19,'2017-05-16 09:05:10',19,'2017-05-26 09:22:21'),
	(46,2,'roca-patrn-tequila-dinner','Roca Patrón Tequila Dinner','<p>DoubleTree Bristol is proud to present a spirited cocktail dinner celebrating Roca Patrón tequila featuring Paul Mazurek, tequila master. Reception at 6:30pm followed by dinner at 7:00pm. Dinner will include a unique 4-course tasting menu prepared by The Willows Executive Chef, to accent each of the five highlighted tequilas: Patrón Mango Tequila Liqueur, Roca Patrón Silver, Roca Patrón Reposado, Roca Patrón Anejo and Patron XO Coffee Liqueur.<br /><br />\nCost is $80 per person (includes tax &amp; gratuity). Reservations are required (credit card needed to hold reservation). Make your reservation today! 860-584-7663.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"/assets/uploads/images/CT_1823596_Doubletree.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Join us on Thursday, July 13 at 6:30pm in The Willows for a very special 4-course tasting menu featuring Roca Patrón Tequila pairings!','2017-07-13',19,'2017-06-01 09:06:58',19,'2017-07-26 15:57:15'),
	(47,2,'wine-wednesdays','Wine Wednesdays','<p>Starting Wednesday, June 6 from 5pm - 10pm, DoubleTree Bristol will be hosting a Wine Wednesday event in TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar, complete with live acoustic music. We will be offering half priced bottles of select wines and a $10 meat and cheese board. We also encourage you to check out our brand new dessert menu, which will pair perfectly with our specially selected wines. </p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/assets/uploads/images/Wine_Wednesdays.jpg\" /></p>\n','Join us every Wednesday in TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar for half priced bottles of wine!','2017-06-06',19,'2017-06-06 09:06:52',19,'2018-04-23 13:53:26'),
	(48,2,'luau-party-on-patio','Luau Party on The Patio','<p>Please join us on Friday, June 16 from 6:30pm - 10pm on The Patio for a special Luau themed party. We will have food and drink specials available and live music by Marty Q. Reservations are not required.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"ing-responsive\" src=\"/assets/uploads/images/martyq6b.jpg\" /></p>\n','Ring in the start of summer at our Luau themed party on The Patio - June 16!','2017-06-16',19,'2017-06-06 09:06:16',19,'2017-06-20 11:03:17'),
	(49,0,'holistic-expo','Holistic Expo','<p>DoubleTree Bristol is looking forward to hosting the Holistic Chamber of Commerce - Connecticut Chapters Passport to Health and Wellness EXPO on Sunday, October 1 from 10am - 5pm. This is an event that is open to the public. For more information and to purchase tickets please visit: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/passport-to-health-and-wellness-fall-2017-tickets-35596313532</p>\n','The CT Holistic Chamber of Commerce Chapters present the Fall 2017 Passport to Health and Wellness EXPO on Sunday, October 1','2017-10-01',19,'2017-09-15 10:09:35',NULL,'2017-09-15 11:06:24'),
	(50,2,'girls-night-out','Girls\' Night Out','<p>It\'s official - Tuesday night is Girls\' Night Out!</p>\n\n<p>Every Tuesday until 10/31, we\'re offering a $35 prix-fixe menu featuring three gourmet courses at The Willows Restaurant. For an additional cost, specially selected wine pairings are also available. It\'s the best deal in Connecticut! To make your reservation, call 860.584.7663 or visit us on OpenTable.</p>\n\n<p>View the full special menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Willows/Girls_Night_Out%5B1%5D.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Every Tuesday evening from September 12 - October 31, DoubleTree\'s chef has a special Prix Fixe menu that makes for an extra-special Girls\' Night Out!','2017-09-12',19,'2017-09-21 09:09:24',NULL,'2017-11-01 15:43:51'),
	(51,2,'nfl-sunday-ticket','NFL Sunday Ticket','<p>Come join us every Sunday from 1pm to close for our Football Sunday All-Day Happy Hour menu. Enjoy happy hour pricing on select food and beverages. We have the NFL Sunday Ticket, so come root on your favorite team!</p>\n\n<p>View our menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/Football_MENU.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n','We have the NFL Sunday Ticket and all day happy hour every Sunday!','2017-10-01',19,'2017-09-25 10:09:27',NULL,'2017-11-01 15:44:08'),
	(52,2,'4th-annual-hopfest','4th Annual HopFest','<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">Enjoy beers from the Northeast and the sounds of Bristol\'s favorite band, Acoustic Marshpit. The partial list of breweries include:</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">Backeast Brewing <br />\nFirefly Brewing<br />\nCity Steam<br />\nSam Adams<br />\nStony Creek<br />\nNew England Brewing Company<br />\nLong Trail<br />\nAlavarium<br />\nConnecticut Beer Tours<br />\nHarpoon<br />\nThimble Island</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">Partial proceeds from ticket sales will benefit the Girl Scouts of Connecticut.</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">Tickets are available in advance at a discount.</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.brownpapertickets.com/event/3091703\">Purchase tickets today!</a></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"> </p>\n','Join us for our 4th Annual HopFest on Saturday, November 11 from 1-5pm. Enjoy tastings from many breweries around the Northeast.','2017-11-11',19,'2017-10-02 15:10:35',19,'2017-10-05 15:48:56'),
	(53,2,'thanksgiving-day-dinner-buffet','Thanksgiving Day Dinner Buffet','<p>Let us handle all of the prep and cleanup, while you and your family kick back and enjoy a special Thanksgiving Day feast!<br /><br />\nThursday, November 23, 2017<br />\n11:30am - 4:30pm<br /><br />\nAdults: $39.95<br />\nChildren under 12: $18<br />\nChildren under 5: FREE<br /><br />\nFor reservations, call 860-584-7673<br /><br />\nFor our menu, click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/2017_Thanksgiving_Menu.pdf\">here</a></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Join us on Thursday, November 23 for a special Thanksgiving Day Dinner Buffet!','2017-11-23',19,'2017-11-01 15:11:00',19,'2017-12-11 08:59:27'),
	(54,2,'host-your-holiday-party-with-us','Host Your Holiday Party With Us','<p>The most wonderful time of the year starts here!<br /><br />\nOur expert event planners are ready to help you plan your holiday party. For more information please call 860.584.7673. Check out our <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/Holiday_Buffet_Menu_2017.pdf\">Holiday Buffet Menu</a> or our <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/Holiday_Served_Menu_2017.pdf\">Holiday Served Menu</a>!<br />\n- Farm fresh cuisine<br />\n- Ballroom and banquet facilities<br />\n- Professional event planners</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Thinking of where to have your holiday party this year? Look no further!','2017-11-03',19,'2017-11-03 13:11:36',NULL,'2018-01-05 15:06:20'),
	(55,2,'timeout-sports-pizza-bar','TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar','<p>We are excited to announce that TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar is officially open. We have a brand new wood fired oven along with a 132\"  laser TV. <br /><br />\nBreakfast will be served in TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar from 6am - 10:30am Monday - Friday and 7am - 11am Saturday - Sunday.<br /><br />\nThe Willows Private Dining Room is available for private functions.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar is officially open!','2018-02-13',19,'2017-11-14 10:11:27',19,'2018-02-16 14:47:31'),
	(56,2,'valentines-day-prix-fixe','Valentine\'s Day Prix Fixe ','<p>We are running a week long Valentine\'s Day dinner special, February 14 - February 17. We have two very special menus for you to choose from. Make your reservation today! 860-589-7766<br /><br /><a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/BDT_01_2018_ValentineMenu-FULL(1).pdf\">Traditional Prix Fixe Menu</a><br /><br /><a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/BDT_01_2018_ValentineMenu-pizza(1).pdf\">Pizza for Two Prix Fixe Menu</a></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Celebrate Valentine\'s Day with us! We have two very special prix fixe menus available.','2018-02-14',19,'2018-01-23 16:01:22',19,'2018-02-19 10:19:38'),
	(57,2,'super-bowl-view-party','Super Bowl View Party','<p>Come out to TimeOut Sports Bar on Sunday, February 4 to watch the NFL Super Bowl on our big screen tv\'s! We will have food and drink specials available all day long. </p>\n','Watch the Super Bowl in TimeOut Sports Bar!','2018-02-04',19,'2018-01-23 16:01:38',NULL,'2018-02-05 15:36:47'),
	(58,2,'city-steam-tap-takeover','City Steam Tap Takeover','<p><span style=\"color:rgb(29,33,41);font-family:\'SF Optimized\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;letter-spacing:-.12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Join us this Friday, February 16 from 5 - 7pm for a City Steam Brewery</span><span style=\"color:rgb(29,33,41);font-family:\'SF Optimized\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;letter-spacing:-.12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"> tap takeover! Beers on tap will be Naughty Nurse Amber Ale, Naughty Nurse IPA, Blonde on Blonde Pale Ale and Jungle Crush IPA. Free giveaways and swag!</span></p>\n','Friday, February 16 5-7pm','2018-02-16',19,'2018-02-12 14:02:51',NULL,'2018-02-19 10:19:26'),
	(59,2,'st-patricks-day-2018','St. Patrick\'s Day 2018','<p>You must have the luck of the Irish - you\'re invited to enjoy an unbeatable St. Patrick\'s Day menu! Join us Friday, March 16 - Sunday, March 18 for a traditional but upscale Irish menu. <br /><br />\nView the full Irish menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/BDT_03_2018_StPatricksDayMenu.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Celebrate St. Patrick\'s Day at DoubleTree Bristol - March 16-18!','2018-03-16',19,'2018-02-19 10:02:08',19,'2018-03-19 09:10:06'),
	(60,2,'2018-basketball-tournament','2018 Basketball Tournament','<p><span style=\"color:rgb(29,33,41);font-family:\'SF Optimized\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;letter-spacing:-.12px;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">The much anticipated March mania college basketball tournament begins on Tuesday, March 13, so fill in your brackets and head to TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar for plenty of game-day food and drink specials! These specials will be available Thursdays - Sundays from 3/15 - 4/2. You\'ll be able to check out our new pizza oven and 160\" Ulta HD 4k video screen! </span></p>\n','Come watch the basketball tournament at TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar!','2018-03-15',19,'2018-02-23 16:02:05',19,'2018-04-10 14:06:56'),
	(61,2,'easter-brunch-2018','Easter Brunch 2018','<p><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">DoubleTree Bristol will be hosting a special Easter Brunch on Sunday, April 1 from 11am - 3pm. Price is $39 for adults and $14 for children under 12. </span><span style=\"font-weight:700;font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;\">Reservations are required - 860.584.7673.</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">We will be serving a wide variety of delicious foods including an omlet station, waffle station, carving station and complimentary mimosa. </span><a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/BDT_04_2017_EasterMenu(1).pdf\" style=\"color:rgb(51,122,183);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;\">Click here to view our full menu.</a></p>\n','Join us for a special Easter Brunch on Sunday, April 1 in The Oaks Ballroom','2018-04-01',19,'2018-03-01 09:03:45',19,'2018-04-02 10:29:59'),
	(62,2,'firefly-hollow-brewing-company-tap-takeover','Firefly Hollow Brewing Company Tap Takeover','<div style=\"font-family:\'SF Optimized\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;color:rgb(29,33,41);font-size:14px;font-style:normal;letter-spacing:-.12px;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\"><span>Beer makes everything better, who agrees with us? </span><span class=\"_3gl1 _5zz4\" style=\"margin-right:1px;margin-left:1px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;background-image:url(&quot;https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f96/1/16/1f37b.png&quot;);height:16px;width:16px;background-position:center;\"><span class=\"_ncl\">','Firefly Hollow Brewing Company Tap Takeover - Friday, April 13','2018-04-13',19,'2018-04-02 10:04:46',NULL,'2018-04-17 14:42:29'),
	(63,2,'mors-day-brunch-2018','Mother\'s Day Brunch 2018','<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia, \'Droid Serif\', serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;line-height:27px;color:rgb(51,51,51);background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Join us from 10am to 2pm on Sunday, May 13 for Mother\'s Day Brunch at DoubleTree Bristol. The menu includes pastries, breakfast items, a Belgian buttermilk waffle station, carving station with oven roasted turkey breast and char grilled flat iron steak; main courses of chicken piccata and parmesan encrusted cod; salads, vegetable sides and a dessert display. Cost is $39 for adults and $14 for children under 12. Reservations are required. 860-584-7673</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia, \'Droid Serif\', serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;line-height:27px;color:rgb(51,51,51);background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">View our Mother\'s Day Brunch menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/BDT_05_2018_MothersDayMenu.pdf\">here</a>.</span></p>\n','Make lasting memories with mom at DoubleTree\'s Mother\'s Day Brunch!','2018-05-13',19,'2018-04-10 14:04:13',NULL,'2018-05-15 09:37:29'),
	(64,2,'happy-hour-at-doubletree','Happy Hour at DoubleTree','<p>We\'ve got one of the best happy hours in Connecticut! Our new menu features specialty cocktails, beers on tap and a variety of delicious bites. To view our complete menu, click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/DTB_04_2018_TOSPB_HappyHour_Menu.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n','Join us every week night from 4-6pm!','2018-04-19',19,'2018-04-19 09:04:34',NULL,'2018-05-02 09:20:43'),
	(65,2,'cinco-de-mayo-2018','Cinco De Mayo 2018','<p><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:\'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;color:rgb(29,33,41);font-size:14px;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span>When life gives you lemons, grab tequila and salt! And join us on Saturday, May 5th for Cinco De Mayo! We will have plenty of food and drink specials all day long including margaritas, Corona buckets, nachos and fish tacos! </span></span></p>\n','Celebrate Cinco De Mayo with us!','2018-05-05',19,'2018-04-23 13:04:13',NULL,'2018-05-08 12:04:17'),
	(66,2,'taco-and-tequila-tuesdays','Taco and Tequila Tuesdays','<p><span style=\"font-style:normal;color:rgb(29,33,41);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Starting May 1, 2018 join us every Tuesday, all day long, for Tacos &amp; Tequila! Our chef will be preparing weekly trendy taco specials along with tequila drinks. Tuesday\'s just got a whole lot better!</span></p>\n','Every Tuesday, join us for weekly taco specials and tequila drinks','2018-05-01',19,'2018-05-02 09:05:00',NULL,'2018-08-29 12:48:37'),
	(67,2,'thursday-night-prix-fixe-dinner','Thursday Night Prix Fixe Dinner','<p>Join us every Thursday evening starting May 3 for a special Girls\' Night Out prix fixe dinner! Our chef will be preparing a 3 course dinner plus a class of house wine for only $30. Reservations are required - 860.584.7663. To view our menu <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/GNO_4X9RackCard_2018_v1.pdf\">click here</a>.</p>\n','3 courses and a glass of house wine - $30!','2018-05-03',19,'2018-05-15 09:05:15',19,'2018-05-31 20:42:59'),
	(68,2,'harpoon-brewery-tap-takeover','Harpoon Brewery Tap Takeover','<p>From 5-7pm on Thursday, May 24 we will have a special Harpoon Brewery Tap Takeover. A representative from the brewery will be answering questions and handing out swag. There will be 4 beers on tap all of which are tailored to summer and warm weather!<br /><br /><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;\">UFO White- Crisp Light bodied Belgium brewed with coriander and orange peel</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;\">Harpoon IPA- hoppy floral and crisp traditional IPA</span></p>\n\n<div style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;\">Harpoon Camp Wannamango- Mango infused pale ale with tropical aroma</span></div>\n\n<div style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:13px;\"> </div>\n\n<div style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:13px;\">Harpoon Limey Vice- Lime Gose, sumer citrusy and tart</div>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Join us on Thursday, May 24 for a Harpoon Brewery Tap Takeover! ','2018-05-24',19,'2018-05-15 11:05:14',NULL,'2018-05-30 09:07:04'),
	(69,2,'2018-friday-night-acoustic-music-summer-series','2018 Friday Night Acoustic Music Summer Series','<p><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Outdoor patio season has officially started in CT! Join us on the Oaks Patio starting Friday, May 25! Every Friday night through September from 6:30pm - 10pm, we will be serving drink and food specials along with live acoustic music performances. <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/DTB27_2018_Live_Music_Schedule_Card_Final.pdf\">View our complete schedule here</a>.</span></p>\n','Join us on the Oaks Patio starting Friday, May 25!','2018-05-25',19,'2018-05-18 10:05:53',NULL,'2018-05-18 10:42:53'),
	(70,2,'fars-day-2018','Father\'s Day 2018','<p>DoubleTree Bristol will be running a ribeye special, June 15 - 22. For $75, we will feature a 32oz Tomahawk Ribeye 32oz steak with roasted potatoes. This will be served with a tarragon bearnase and chimichurri sauce. A wine pairing can be included at an additional fee. This special will be served during lunch and dinner, either inside or outside on our patio.<br /><br />\nBreakfast will have extended hours until 12pm on Sunday, June 16 with specials available.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Celebrate Dad with a special Tomahawk Ribeye special June 15 - 22!','2018-06-15',19,'2018-06-01 10:06:59',NULL,'2018-06-25 13:49:21'),
	(71,2,'two-roads-tap-takeover','Two Roads Tap Takeover','<p>Calling all beer lovers! We will be having a tap takeover by Two Roads Brewing Company on Thursday, June 21 from 5-7pm. A representive from the brewery will be on site to answer questions and hand out swag. There will be four beers on tap:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><li>Two Juicy- Unfiltered Double IPA</li>\n	<li>Road Jam- Raspberry Wheat</li>\n	<li>No Limits- Hefeweizen</li>\n	<li>Persian Lime Gose-Ale Brewed with Persian Lime</li>\n</ul><p> </p>\n','Join us on June 21 for a Two Roads tap takeover!','2018-06-21',19,'2018-06-06 13:06:28',NULL,'2018-06-25 13:49:14'),
	(72,2,'national-prosecco-week','National Prosecco Week','<p>Calling all Prosecco lovers! We will be celebrating National Prosecco Week with a week long special menu of foods that pair nicely with processco. These items will be available June 11 - 16 and can be enjoyed on our outdoor patio or inside TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar. <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/DTB_NatProseccoWeek_5X7TableTent_150dpi.pdf\">View our complete menu here.</a></p>\n','Join us for National Prosecco Week June 11 - 16','2018-06-11',19,'2018-06-08 10:06:53',NULL,'2018-06-18 11:29:40'),
	(73,2,'thimble-island-tap-takeover','Thimble Island Tap Takeover','<p>Join us on Thursday, July 12 from 5-7pm for an exciting tap takeover from Thimble Island Brewery. Weather permitting, we will be hosting this event on our outdoor patio. There will be 4 beers on tap including: Ruby Tart Blonde Ale, American Amber Ale and Island Hopper IPA. The fourth surprise will either be a special summer offering or session IPA. A brewery representative will be on site to answer any questions and will be handing out free giveways including a pint glass for all attendees.<br /><br />\nWe will also have live acoustic music from Bailey Jeffko. We hope to see you there!</p>\n','Thimble Island Brewery Tap Takeover July 12 on our Patio!','2018-07-12',19,'2018-06-26 15:06:48',19,'2018-07-18 14:23:33'),
	(74,2,'shark-week-specials','Shark Week Specials','<p>Calling all shark week lovers! DoubleTree Bristol has some bite-worthy food &amp; drink specials to make your dining experience extra fin-tastic! These specials will be available July 22-28 for lunch and dinner, to be enjoyed inside our TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar or outside on our patio. <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/DTB_SharkWeek_4X5TableTent.pdf\">View our complete menu here.</a></p>\n','Bite-worthy food &amp; drink specials July 22-28','2018-07-22',19,'2018-07-10 15:07:18',NULL,'2018-08-01 09:21:15'),
	(75,2,'beats-by-bailey','Beats by Bailey','<p>Please join us for live acoustic music from Bailey Jeffko, the first and last Thursday of every month. Bailey will be performing from 6-8pm and we will have our Happy Hour menu available along with half price wines from 5-8pm. Weather pending, we will be hosting these events on our outdoor patio but will move inside to TimeOut Sports &amp; Pizza Bar in bad weather.</p>\n','Live acoustic music from Bailey Jeffko, the first and last Thursday of every month!','2018-08-02',19,'2018-08-01 09:08:13',NULL,'2018-09-21 19:24:43'),
	(76,2,'thomas-hooker-brewery-tap-takeover','Thomas Hooker Brewery Tap Takeover','<p>We are excited to be hosting a Thomas Hooker Brewery Tap Takeover on Thursday, August 30 from 5-7pm. A representative from the brewery will be on site to answer any questions and will be handing out swag and other giveaways. Beers on tap will include Nectar of the Goats - Pale Ale, Blonde Ale, Ode to Blumpy - IPA and Super Dooper - Double IPA.</p>\n','Join us Thursday, August 30 5-7pm!','2018-08-30',19,'2018-08-08 12:08:26',19,'2018-09-04 13:04:42'),
	(77,3,'nfl-sunday-ticket-2018-19','NFL Sunday Ticket 2018-19','<p>Need a place to watch every NFL game this season? Look no further! DoubleTree Bristol has the NFL Sunday Ticket. We have a beautiful 160\" HDTV along with 12 beers on tap and weekly food and beverage specials. Come watch the playoffs and the Super Bowl here!<br />\n </p>\n','Watch all of the games on our 160\" HDTV!','2018-09-06',19,'2018-08-29 12:08:57',19,'2019-01-02 10:43:29'),
	(78,3,'half-price-wine-wednesdays','Half Price Wine Wednesdays','<p style=\"font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Cambria, Georgia, serif;font-size:14.666666984558105px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria, Georgia, serif;font-size:14.666666984558105px;font-style:normal;\">Join us every Wednedsay evening for half price bottles of select wine to be enjoyed with our happy hour menu or our regular food menu. View our complete list of discounted wine bottles </span><a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/BDT_09_2018_Wine-Menu_03.pdf\" style=\"font-family:Cambria, Georgia, serif;font-size:14.666666984558105px;font-style:normal;\">here</a><span style=\"font-family:Cambria, Georgia, serif;font-size:14.666666984558105px;font-style:normal;\">.</span></p>\n\n<p><br />\nHere is our live acoustic music schedule:</p>\n\n<div style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Cambria, Georgia, serif;font-size:14.666666984558105px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria, Georgia, serif;font-size:14.666666984558105px;font-style:normal;\">January 11th - Wayne Patrick Brown Band<br />\nJanuary 16th - Brendan Donahue<br />\nJanuary 23rd - Jeff Przech<br />\nJanuary 30th - Tom Scarola                       </span></div>\n\n<p> </p>\n','Half price bottles of select wine!','2018-09-05',19,'2018-09-04 13:09:02',19,'2019-01-02 10:40:35'),
	(79,0,'blue-point-brewing-company-tap-takeover','Blue Point Brewing Company Tap Takeover','<p><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:\'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;color:rgb(29,33,41);font-size:14px;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span>Please join us on Thursday, September 27 from 5-7pm for a fun and exciting tap takeover from </span></span><span class=\"_247o\" style=\"font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(220,230,248);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;color:rgb(29,33,41);font-size:14px;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span><span>Blue Point Brewery</span></span></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:\'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', \'system-ui\', sans-serif;color:rgb(29,33,41);font-size:14px;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span>! Featured beers will be Toasted Lager, Oktoberfest, Pumpkin Ale and Tropical Hoptical Illusion IPA. A representative from the brewery will be on site to answer questions and hand out tshirts, coasters, hats, key chains and glasses. Weather permitting, this event will be held on our outdoor patio. We hope to see you there!</span></span></p>\n','Join us Thursday, September 27 5-7pm!','2018-09-27',19,'2018-09-21 19:09:45',NULL,'2018-10-11 14:17:14'),
