	(84,2,'fall-prix-fixe-dinner','Fall Prix Fixe Dinner','<p>Please join us for a special Fall 3-course prix-fixe dinner Sunday, October 21 thru Saturday, November 17. Choose from an appetizer, main course and dessert plus a glass of house wine. <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/TimeOut-Patio/FallPrixFixeDinner_4X5TableTent_v2.pdf\">Our full menu can be found here</a>. Reservations are strong encouraged. Please call 860-584-7663.</p>\n','$30 3-course dinner 10/21 - 11/17','2018-10-21',19,'2018-09-28 11:09:03',19,'2018-11-19 09:33:32'),
	(85,2,'2018-thanksgiving-day-dinner-buffet','2018 Thanksgiving Day Dinner Buffet','<p><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Let us handle all of the prep and cleanup, while you and your family kick back and enjoy a special Thanksgiving Day feast!</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Thursday, November 22, 2018</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">11:30am - 4:30pm</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Adults: $39.95</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Children under 12: $18</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Children under 5: FREE</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">For reservations, call 860-584-7673</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">For our menu, click <a href=\"/assets/uploads/files/Ballroom/DTB_2018ThanksgivingRackCard_v2.pdf\">here</a></span></p>\n','Join us on Thursday, November 22 for a special Thanksgiving Day Dinner Buffet!','2018-11-22',19,'2018-10-08 13:10:52',NULL,'2018-10-08 13:25:52'),
	(86,2,'st-killian-importing-tap-takeover','St. Killian Importing Tap Takeover','<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Please join us on Thursday, December 6 from <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">5-7pm for a Tap Takeover by </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">St. Killian Importing. St. Killian is an import company that brings in beer from other countries! </span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">The four beers that will be featured are:<br />\nCarlsberg- Pilsner</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Kronenbourg 1664 Blanc - Witbier</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Young\'s - Double Chocolate Stout</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Haufbrauhaus Traunstein - Festbier (Octoberfest)</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">We will have a representative on site to answer any questions, who will also be handing out plenty of swag. We hope to see you there!</p>\n','Thursday, December 6    5-7pm','2018-12-06',19,'2018-11-19 09:11:30',19,'2018-12-14 11:48:40'),
	(87,2,'national-cookie-day','National Cookie Day','<p>December 4, 2018 is National Cookie Day! In honor of this special day, we are giving away our signature chocolate chip cookies for anyone who stops in. No purchase required.</p>\n','#NationalCookieDay','2018-12-04',19,'2018-11-27 11:11:47',NULL,'2018-11-27 11:17:47'),
	(88,2,'2018-holiday-parties','2018 Holiday Parties','<p><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Our expert event planners are ready to help you plan your holiday party. For more information please call 860.584.7673. </span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">- Farm fresh cuisine</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">- Ballroom and banquet facilities</span><br style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-style:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">- Professional event planners</span></p>\n','The most wonderful time of the year starts here!','2018-12-04',19,'2018-12-04 21:12:57',NULL,'2018-12-04 21:21:57'),
	(89,2,'local-beer-night','Local Beer Night','<p>Please join us on Thursday, December 27 for a local beer night. <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Our taps will be having multiple offerings of beers made from CT breweries.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">Offerings: Not finalized but will most likely include:</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;\">Counter Weight- Headway IPA</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Backeast- Limited IPA release</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Seasonal Beer Offering (most likely winter lager)</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">City Steam- Naughty Nurse</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Stony Creek- Joe (Stout)</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Two Roads- Two Juicy- Double IPA</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thomas Hooker- Super Duper- Double IPA </p>\n','Thursday, December 27 5pm - midnight','2018-12-27',19,'2018-12-14 11:12:10',NULL,'2019-01-02 10:37:56'),
